he field,\nwe find that the ML-based model doubles the F1 score of human experts in its\nability to identify fast Li-ion conductors from atomistic structure with a\nthousand- fold increase in speed, clearly demonstrating the utility of this\nmodel for the research community. All conducting materials reported here lack\ntransition metals and are predicted to exhibit low electronic conduction, high\nstability against oxidation, and high thermodynamic stability.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 7 Aug 2018 17:33:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-04-22"}
