45 \\pm 0.05\\, R_\\odot$, $0.10 \\pm 0.06\\,\nL_\\odot$, respectively. The marginal contact, together with the period\ndecrease, suggests that this binary system may be at a key evolutionary stage,\nas predicted by the theory of thermal relaxation oscillations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 7 Aug 2018 22:12:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-08-29"}
