 TNO discoveries from future\nwell-characterized surveys. We show that a deeper survey (to a limiting\nr-magnitude of 26.0) with a similar survey area to OSSOS could statistically\ndistinguish between these five Neptune migration models.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 8 Aug 2018 04:16:05 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 24 Apr 2019 22:55:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-07-17"}
