rom pre-enriched material. Analysis of auxiliary data shows that\nthe dwarf galaxy candidate is composed of material originating from NGC 4634.\nWe cannot determine whether this material has been ejected tidally or through\nother processes, which makes the system highly interesting for follow up\nobservations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 8 Aug 2018 14:38:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-11-28"}
